        <h2>Architectural principle</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Decisions live in main context. Subagents only execute pre-decided recipes in parallel. The baseline ships exactly one subagent: <code>swarm-worker</code>. It runs <code>scenario</code> then <code>implement</code> against a fully-specified recipe inside an isolated git worktree, and never makes design choices.</p>
